title: JRE Review of 1284 with Graham Hancock
description:
Graham has a new book out and is a historian investigator of sorts. He travels the world looking at ancient sites to see if our current history knowledge aligns with what he finds. His conversations with Joe are always really thought provoking so make sure to listen to this one to the end.

 

Enjoy my review folks!
